Package: cv2r
Title: Use OpenCV in RStudio 
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Emmanuel", "BATT", email = "battmanu@free.fr", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: All it does is to import cv2 from python through reticulate and overload imshow so that the output can be visualised in the Viewer pane.
